{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "小马与常无意夜探蓝兰房间，发现空轿，蓝兰随后现身小马房中，二人发生亲密关系。蓝兰带小马去看弟弟蓝寄云——一个病入膏肓的年轻人。次日珍珠姐妹与老皮失踪，众人焦急等待。一名因食用麻草而精神失常的少女出现，透露法师吃人的恐怖事实。郝生意解释麻草之害。最后，一位看似慈祥的老人现身太平客栈，正是食人法师本人，暗示危险逼近。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你刚才看见的不是鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可是我们真的遇见个女鬼！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "蓝兰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "她不但是个女鬼，还是个狐狸精！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你看她这么样做究竟是什么目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我也看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "所以我们现在就应该回去睡觉，假装根本不知道这回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "刚才你到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我喝得太多，总得放点出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在还可以再放一点出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你不睡在自己房里，到我这里来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我一个人睡不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我睡得着！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你是不是在生气，生谁的气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "难道你也怕常剥皮剥你的皮？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是他只说过不许男人碰女人，并没有说不许女人碰男人，所以…，",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在我就要来碰你了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "难怪别人说你是条驴子你真的是！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轿子里为什么没有人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你是不是想看看我二弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "只可惜我看不见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那只因为他并不在你去看的那顶轿子里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他在我房里那顶轿子里，他病得很重，我对他不能不特别小心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我故意将一顶空轿子摆在最好的那间客房里，却将他抬入了我的房，我到这里来的时候，就叫珍珠姐妹去守着他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "好，我带你去见见他！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这是我弟弟，他叫蓝寄云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这就是拼了命也要保护我们过山的小马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ji_yun",
      "speaker_name": "蓝寄云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_ji_yun",
      "text": "你……你多保重。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我不是驴子，我是个猪！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你不是。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我是！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你又不肥，怎么会是猪？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我是个瘦猪！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我知道你的心事，我心里也很难受，可是…。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是只要我们能保证他平安过山，我们……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我若做不到这件事，我自己一头就撞死！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你还在生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我不是在生你的气。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你在生谁的气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我再三吩咐，叫她们守在这里，可是现在她们居然连人影子都看不见了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "就算她们有什么急事，也不该两个人一起走的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "也许她们很快会回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我早就说过他根本不是人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "但我却保证，珍珠姐妹绝不是被他拐走的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他还没有这么大的本事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你还记不记得那个有双漂亮大腿的女孩子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你还记不记得她说的话？只要我们去找她，她随时都欢迎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那女人实在是个魔女，我若是男人，说不定也会忍不住要去找她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我早应该知道他们受不了这种诱惑的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "多了他们三个人并不算多，少了他们三个人也不算少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "难道你准备就这样把他们抛下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "难道你还想去找他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你还想不想过山？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你长得真好看，我喜欢好看的男人，我喜欢…我喜欢。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "text": "你受了伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我没有，我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "text": "这血是哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这不是血，是我的奶，我要给我的宝贝吃奶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你猜我的另一半到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "到法师肚子里去了，他是我的宝贝，他喜欢吃我的奶，我也喜欢给他吃。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "speaker_name": "嬉狼女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我也喜欢你，你也是我的宝贝，我也要给你吃我的奶。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_lang_nv",
      "text": "我本来不该这么对你的，可是我想不出别的法子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "好好的一个女孩子，为什么偏偏要吃草？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "她吃草？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "吃得很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "吃什么的人我都见过，可是吃草的人……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "她吃的不是普通的那种草。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "是哪种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是那种要命的毒药。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这里的山阴后长着种麻草，不管谁吃了后，都会变得疯疯颠颠、痴痴迷迷的，就好象……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "就好像喝醉酒一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "比喝醉酒还可怕十倍。一个人酒醉时心里总算还有三分清醒，吃了这种麻草后，就变得什么事都不知道，什么事都会做得出了",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "吃这种草也有瘾？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "据说他们那些人一天不吃都不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "他们那些人是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是群总觉得什么事都不对劲，什么人都看不顺眼的大孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你见过法师？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "什么人的肉他都吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "如果他有儿子，说不定也已被他吃下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "这种人居然还能活在现在，倒是怪事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你若有个儿子女儿被他吃了下去，你就会奇怪他为什么还不死了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "就算我有个儿女被他吃了下去，我也只有走远些看着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为我不想被他们吃下去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_shi",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_fa_shi",
      "text": "你老人家今天还是喝茶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_shi",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_fa_shi",
      "text": "今天你老人家是喝香片，还是喝龙井？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_shi",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "随便什么都行，只要浓点，今天我吃得太多太腻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_shi",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看见年轻的女孩子，我总难免会多吃一点儿的，小姑娘的肉不但好吃，而且滋补得狠。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    }
